tion box end}}\n\n==Personal life==\nGohmert and his wife Kathy are parents to three daughters. Gohmert attends [[Green Acres Baptist Church]] in Tyler, where he has served as a deacon and teaches Sunday school.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gohmert.house.gov/Biography/ |title=Biography: U.S. Congressman Louie Gohmert |publisher=Gohmert.house.gov |accessdate=April 13, 2012}}</ref> Gohmert is a [[Southern Baptist]].<ref name=Baptist>{{cite news|title=Ten Southern Baptists sworn in as new reps.|url=http://www.bpnews.net/bpnews.asp?id=34378|accessdate=December 25, 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226010629/http://www.bpnews.net/34378|archivedate=December 26, 2014|newspaper=Baptist Press|date=January 5, 2011}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Conspiracy theories]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n{{Portalbar|Texas|United States Army|Politics|Conservatism|Baptist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{sisterlinks|d=Q532647|n=no|b=no|v=no|voy=no|m=no|mw=no|wikt=no|s=Author:Louis_Buller_Gohmert|c=Category:Louie_Gohmert}}\n* [http://gohmert.house.gov/ Congressman Louis Gohmert] official congressional website\n* {{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Texas/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Louie_Gohmert_%5BR-1%5D}}\n* [http://www.texastribune.org/directory/louie-gohmert Profile], texastribune.org\n* {{C-SPAN|Louie Gohmert}}\n;Articles\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20070814212804/http://www.vfw.org/index.cfm?fa=news.magDtl&dtl=3&mid=2305 \"Nine New Veterans Join Congress\"], [[Veterans of Foreign Wars]] Magazine\n* {{YouTube|G6nR7mgjfmE|Video of Gohmert criticizing Rep. John Murtha}}\n* [http://thinkprogress.org/2007/02/28/murtha-market video of Gohmert Blaming Stock Market Failures on Democrats]\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-par|us-hs}}\n{{USRepSuccessionBox\n| state=Texas\n| district=1\n| before=[[Max Sandlin]]\n| start=2005\n}}\n|-\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Virginia Foxx]]<br>R-[[North Carolina]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=''[[List of current members of the United Sta